  <brief_title>The Rilpivirine Cerebrospinal-fluid (CSF) Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Pharmacokinetic Study to Assess the Cerebrospinal-fluid (CSF) Exposure of Rilpivirine in HIV-infected Subjects Switching From TDF/FTC/Nevirapine to TDF/FTC/Rilpivirine</official_title>
